        <abstract> 
<p>Asks that a copy of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> be sent to Thomas Rivers.</p>  
<p>Curious about sale of <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>. It is too stiff for the public. "If praise from Botanists would sell, it would go off well."</p> 
        </abstract>
